power your students with life skills while teaching simple effective yoga tools to support learning and achievement in your classroom.";i:32;s:126:"Our Chair Yoga for Teens manual equips you with a wide variety of grade-appropriate yoga breathing poses games and relaxation.";i:33;s:129:"Plant the seeds for life skills while teaching simple effective yoga tools to support learning and achievement in your classroom.";i:34;s:129:"Our Chair Yoga for Children manual equips you with a wide variety of grade-appropriate yoga breathing poses games and relaxation.";i:35;s:60:"Youll have enough tools to simply use for yoga breaks or if.";i:36;s:103:"We found a fantastic 30 minute routine of gentle chair yoga for seniors thats free to watch on YouTube.";i:37;s:103:"Instructor Sherry Zak Morris makes the class fun and lively and explains the benefits of the movements.";i:38;s:131:"We share customization and safety tips and give an overview of the movements included in this 30 minute at-home chair yoga routine.";i:39;s:115:"The majority of yoga poses in a chair yoga sequence on the other hand take place from a seated position in a chair.";i:40;s:178:"Depending on the mobility of the class a yoga teacher might include a pose or two that involves standing up perhaps using stabilizing hands on the chair to aid and train balance.";i:41;s:56:"A Chair Yoga Sequence for the Whole Body and Mind Photo.";i:42;s:62:"Rogers Chair yoga is one of the most democratic forms of yoga.";i:43;s:32:"Its accessible to almost anyone.";i:44;s:82:"Try this chair yoga sequence designed by Jivana Heyman to reduce joint strain and.";i:45;s:115:"Chair Yoga invites you to find mobility in a way that is soft and gentle but also really supportive and beneficial.";i:46;s:102:"This 17 min practice invites awareness and integrity into the body specifically the line of the spine.";i:47;s:103:"Activate the muscles that help you find length up through the spine for better posture and energy flow.";i:48;s:14:"August 1